                     <hi rend="largeCaps">HENRY BROWN</hi> (18)</persName>, was indicted<rs id="t18680706-631-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18680706-631-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18680706-631-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp> for embezzlement.</rs>
